(defvar tcode-transpose-strokes-enable-commands
  '(tcode-self-insert-command
    egg-self-insert-command
    self-insert-command
    tcode-transpose-strokes-or-chars)
  "*次の動作でストロークを入れ替えることができるコマンドのリスト。
